comment_data.body: with the other fixes, the timeout doesn't really need to be raised but raising it anyway just to be safe.
@jakemac53 please let me know if you clean this up and just make the scheme bazel://
This class wasn't ever used and doesn't seem compatible with current implementations.

Perhaps add a todo here that we anticipate a future change to this url scheme?
Is this change part of another modifying the settings page?
This was a bug fix for my previous cl. Added a comment clarifying what it is doing.
